name: Jeremy McMasters
text: Great take and bake pizza. The prices are a little bit higher than frozen pizzas at the store but they are made fresh right in front of you with fresh ingredients. The staff is friendly and gives you quick service.

name: Chris Mealer
text: I have had every pizza on the menu and I love them all. Best pizza I have ever had. High quality ingredients.  Clean place and very fast service

name: Michael Gardner
text: Very clean shop and very nice and helpful workers! The pizza was delicious!! I particularly love the crust and fresh vegetables!! I will definitely be back for more

name: Tracy Thurman
text: Waiting way too long :( Ours at home in Indiana is much faster!

name: Iconic Baby
text: They gave us the wrong pizza we don't eat VEGATARIAN PIZZA

name: Jack Brown
text: Great customer service and a tasty product
